### 向指定聊天对象发送文本消息
POST http://localhost:9999/wxSend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "文件传输助手",
  "content": "Hello, World!"
}

### 向指定聊天对象发送远程文件（http/https）
POST http://localhost:9999/wxSend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "文件传输助手",
  "file": "https://example.com/file.pdf"
}

### 向指定聊天对象发送本地文件
POST http://localhost:9999/wxSend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "文件传输助手",
  "file": "C:\\Users\\User\\Documents\\test.txt"
}

### 测试微信窗口状态
GET http://localhost:9999/test
